# curated public results docs, which are ALL `.md`. By default these belong in the
# private notes repo (../fak-private), the same as a session's brainstorm/audit notes.
# Ignoring the `.txt` class here makes that the default: a stray status note can never be
# `git add`-ed into this public tree by accident (same private-by-default guard pattern
# as the bench-node run dirs further below). Curated `.md` benchmark docs stay tracked.
docs/benchmarks/*.txt

