# output (written by tools/industry_freshness_cadence.py). The SCRIPTS are tracked; the
# state they emit is not — same private-by-default guard as the bench-node run dirs below.
# Root-level *_out.txt / *_err.txt are shell stdout/stderr redirects from ad-hoc
